DR. NEWSOME.

906
00:40:01,132 --> 00:40:03,602
I'M ASSUMING YOUR FIRM GRASP
ON REALITY

907
00:40:03,635 --> 00:40:05,735
MEANS THAT YOU'RE TAKING
YOUR MEDS.

908
00:40:05,771 --> 00:40:07,011
YEAH,
I THOUGHT A PILL A DAY

909
00:40:07,038 --> 00:40:08,638
WAS SUPPOSED TO KEEP
THE DOCTOR AWAY.

910
00:40:08,674 --> 00:40:10,744
MAX TOLD ME
WHERE TO FIND YOU.

911
00:40:10,776 --> 00:40:14,776
I CAME BY TO SAY
THAT THE MEDS AREN'T ENOUGH.

912
00:40:14,813 --> 00:40:16,113
IF YOU WANT
TO STAY HEALTHY,

913
00:40:16,147 --> 00:40:17,547
YOU'RE GONNA NEED
REGULAR TALK THERAPY.

914
00:40:17,583 --> 00:40:18,853
AND APPARENTLY,
YOU MAKE HOUSE CALLS.

915
00:40:18,884 --> 00:40:22,054
ACTUALLY,
I'VE BEEN THINKING.

916
00:40:22,087 --> 00:40:25,017
GIVEN YOUR
LONG-STANDING...

917
00:40:25,056 --> 00:40:27,456
RELATIONSHIP WITH NATALIE,

918
00:40:27,493 --> 00:40:29,733
I DON'T THINK
IT'S APPROPRIATE

919
00:40:29,761 --> 00:40:31,801
FOR ME TO CONTINUE TO BE
YOUR PSYCHIATRIST.

920
00:40:31,830 --> 00:40:34,000
WELL, MAYBE YOU CAN
RECOMMEND SOMEBODY

921
00:40:34,032 --> 00:40:35,932
WHO'S NOT
AN INSUFFERABLE BORE.

922
00:40:35,967 --> 00:40:39,197
JUST BECAUSE I CAN'T BE
YOUR DOCTOR

923
00:40:39,237 --> 00:40:42,737
DOESN'T MEAN
I CAN'T BE YOUR FRIEND.

924
00:40:42,774 --> 00:40:46,114
IF YOU NEED ONE.

925
00:40:49,214 --> 00:40:51,854
I CAN'T HELP WONDERING...

926
00:40:51,883 --> 00:40:54,153
IF I HAD ACTUALLY
HAD THE NERVE

927
00:40:54,185 --> 00:40:56,915
TO APPROACH YOU
ALL THOSE YEARS AGO,

928
00:40:56,955 --> 00:40:59,855
WOULD YOU HAVE GIVEN ME
THE TIME OF DAY?

929
00:41:00,992 --> 00:41:04,132
I DON'T KNOW.

930
00:41:04,162 --> 00:41:06,732
BUT ONE THING YOU'LL FIND OUT
PRETTY QUICK

931
00:41:06,765 --> 00:41:08,865
IS THAT I'M NOBODY'S
FANTASY GIRL.

932
00:41:13,939 --> 00:41:16,609
47 ACROSS -- PARASOL.

933
00:41:20,879 --> 00:41:21,979
[ CLEARS THROAT ]

934
00:41:22,013 --> 00:41:23,723
UM, IF WE'RE
GONNA BE FRIENDS,

935
00:41:23,749 --> 00:41:25,719
ONE THING YOU'LL FIGURE OUT
PRETTY QUICK

936
00:41:25,751 --> 00:41:27,751
IS THAT I MAY NEED HELP
ONCE IN A WHILE,

937
00:41:27,786 --> 00:41:30,256
BUT I REALLY HATE IT WHEN PEOPLE
GIVE ME THE ANSWERS.

938
00:41:30,288 --> 00:41:33,628
SOMETIMES
THE BILLIONS OF NEURONS

939
00:41:33,659 --> 00:41:38,699
FIRING IN OUR BRAINS HELP US
CONCOCT ELABORATE SCENARIOS.

940
00:41:38,730 --> 00:41:42,870
WE IMAGINE OURSELVES
WITH A DREAM GIRL

941
00:41:42,901 --> 00:41:44,841
OR LANDING A DREAM JOB --

942
00:41:44,870 --> 00:41:48,610
AN ASTRONAUT, ROCK STAR,

943
00:41:48,640 --> 00:41:50,880
EVEN A UNITED STATES SENATOR.

944
00:41:50,909 --> 00:41:54,749
BUT FANTASIES CAN TURN DARK.

945
00:41:54,780 --> 00:41:59,150
WE START TO BELIEVE
THERE'S A MONSTER UNDER THE BED

946
00:41:59,184 --> 00:42:03,994
OR THAT EVIL FORCES ARE ALIGNING
THEMSELVES AGAINST US.

947
00:42:04,022 --> 00:42:06,962
ALL THESE FANTASIES --
GOOD AND BAD --

948
00:42:06,992 --> 00:42:09,902
STEM FROM
AN EVOLUTIONARY IMPERATIVE.

949
00:42:09,928 --> 00:42:13,158
OUR BRAINS ARE EXPLORING
POTENTIAL OUTCOMES

950
00:42:13,198 --> 00:42:17,168
THAT MIGHT HELP US ACHIEVE
OUR GOALS OR AVOID DANGER.

951
00:42:17,202 --> 00:42:21,672
BUT IF WE ALLOW FANTASY
TO OVERTAKE OUR THINKING...

952
00:42:24,209 --> 00:42:29,919
...WE CAN MISS THE REALITY
THAT'S RIGHT IN FRONT OF US.

953
00:42:29,948 --> 00:42:33,178
AND SOMETIMES...

954
00:42:33,218 --> 00:42:37,088
REALITY'S NOT SO BAD.

